_sText:
***Changes in the Final Version (19.02.2012)***

- made the whole map larger for better gameplay experience
- added ladders
- decreased the volume of the waterfalls
- removed the chatadvertisements cause they annoyed players

Iam done with the final version of this map, if there are any bugs that i forgot to fix or did not see, make a comment or add me in Steam.
I will try to fix it as soon as possible.
Its my first map. so dont judge to hard :-)

How to play my map:
My map is a norush map. If you try to rush you get teleported to a jail! Terrorists and Counterterrorists have their own. If someone is afk you can use the bridge to go on the other side (only way to rush).

ok have fun with it, i hope you like it

Steam: [bonebraker18](http://steamcommunity.com/id/bonebraker18 "ADD ME")
